propertyName.ja: 車載電池の放電可能容量値1
propertyName.en: Dischargeable capacity of vehicle mounted battery 1

note.ja: 車載電池の放電可能容量値1 は、電気自動車充放電器に接続された電気自動車から出力される場合、搭載を必須とする。応答できない状況にある場合、不可応答を返す。
note.en: The installation of "Dischargeable capacity of vehicle mounted battery 1" is mandatory in case of output from an electric vehicle connected to an electric vehicle charger/discharger. Where no response can be returned, "Response impossible" is returned.

state.en: purchasing power designated electric energy charging

note.ja: 運転モード設定(EPC=0xDA)に充電(0x42)，充放電（0x46）を設定した時の充電方式を示す。
note.en: This property indicates the charging method when setting charging (0x42) and charging/discharging (0x46) to the operation mode setting (EPC=0xDA).

state.en: purchasing power designated electric energy discharging

note.ja: 運転モード設定(EPC=0xDA)に放電(0x43)，充放電（0x46）を設定した時の放電方式を示す。
note.en: This property indicates discharging method when setting discharging (0x43) to operation mode setting (EPC=0xDA), and discharging method when setting charging/discharging (0x46)

note.ja: 買電電力の上限値をW で指定する。充電方式が買電電力指定充電（0x05）または放電方式が買電電力指定放電(0x05)の場合有効になる
note.en: This property specifies the highest value of the purchasing power electric energy in W. This shall be activated when charging method is purchasing power designated electric energy discharging (0x05), or discharging method is purchasing power designated electric energy charging (0x05).
